1 The emotional impact of this movie defies words . It is elegant , subtle , beautiful , and tragic all rolled into two hours . This is Will Smith as he matures into his acting ability , the full range of it . Who knew ? I saw The Pursuit of Happiness and thought , this must be a fluke for the blockbuster , over - the - top actor , Smith . His performances in both movies portray a whole other dimension to Smith , a refinement of talent , the selectivity of scripts , I 'm not sure , but I view him differently now . Seven Pounds is one of those movies that in order to fully enjoy its essence you have to suspend your belief . Do n't watch it for the plot , watch it for the fragile condition of the human heart , both literally and metaphorically . It is a story of human guilt , atonement , love , and sacrifice .
